added.title: Halloween vs. Christmas
added.description: When Santa tries to take over Halloween, it's up to the Titans and a few ghouls to stop him.

added.title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
added.description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

added.title: Christmas Crusaders
added.description: Santa Claus and Robin must stop the nefarious Coal Miner.

added.title: Toddler Titans...Yay!
added.description: Control Freak thinks the Titans' humor is too juvenile for their time-slot, so he ages them down to a preschool show.

added.title: Huggbees
added.description: The Brain teams up with The Lobe, so the Titans enlist the help of Freakazoid to stop them.

added.title: Baby Mouth
added.description: In order to find out about his family history, Robin takes a DNA test and discovers he's from Babylon.

added.title: Franken-Fight
added.description: Ben hops into the Rustbuggy for a driving lesson along the sand dunes of Cape Cod, but he takes a freaky switchback turn when the Rustbuggy is mutated into a motor-monster by Bootleg, another alien transformation of Kevin 11, with powers similar to Upgrade!

added.title: Buggin' the Buggs
added.description: Team Tennyson travel to the Chrysalen Institute for some hot yoga and good vibes, only to find that the Bugg Brothers are on vacation, too, but are the sneaky insectoids really on holiday, or just cooking up yet another silly, yet high stakes scheme?

added.title: Which Watch
added.description: After a battle with Kevin gets mysteriously cut short, Ben turns his attention to one upping Gwen at Space Camp. But, when his arch-nemesis, Kevin, returns with his sights strangely set on his cousin, our hero must uncover who is really behind it all, Charmcaster!

added.title: Baby Buktu
added.description: When attacked in the jungle, Team Tennyson is saved by a toddler who looks eerily similar to Tim Buktu, but when they discover it really is a pint sized version of the nefarious globetrotter, Ben knows there's another threat looming, Nanny Nightmare!

added.title: Them's Fightin' Words!
added.description: After enjoying some local corn, Team Tennyson discovers a Hartfield-McJoy reenactment in the cornfield next door, but when Hex resurrects the ghosts of the real feuding families, Ben must find a way to bring them together if he is to save the day!

added.title: Gobble Head
added.description: Chef accidentally cooks up a killer cyborg turkey in a failed attempt to get the kids to appreciate him on Appreciation Day.

added.title: Stingin' in the Rain
added.description: When Chef gets locked outside in a storm, the kids mistakenly assume he's a robber and decide to protect the Daycare, by any means necessary.

added.title: Cartoon Realism
added.description: Gwen is frustrated by Beth's silly belief that cartoons are real, but they visit an animation studio and discover that Beth is right!

added.title: OWW
added.description: When the kids discover Chef's past as a disgraced pro wrestler, they invite his old tag team partner to help put on a charity show. But is the big match about re-union or re-venge?!?

added.title: That's a Wrap
added.description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

added.title: Dungeon Crawl!
added.description: Having joined forces with the Lowly in their quest to defeat King Vangelis, Cole, Wu, and Vania have to find a way out of the bottom of the mountain, a place said to be inescapable.

added.title: Grief Bringer
added.description: Nya and Kai, who have become the respective leaders of the Munce and Geckles, attempt to unite the tribes in an effort to defeat their mutual enemy, the Skull Sorcerer, who schemes against them.

added.title: Masters Never Quit
added.description: Pursued by a magma monster, Cole, Princess Vania, Wu & the Lowly arrive at a mysterious temple deep in Shintaro Mountain, a temple which was once a training ground for Earth Elementals including Cole's own mother, Lilly!

added.title: The Darkest Hour
added.description: Forced to flee by the arrival of Grief-Bringer, the ninja, the Munce and the Geckles take refuge in the Geckle Strong-Cave. But the bitter feud between Munce and Geckles threatens to tear them apart, just when unity is needed most…when they are about to confront the Skull Sorcerer and Grief-Bringer!

added.title: The Ascent
added.description: Cole, the Lowly, Princess Vania and Wu discover that the stone-mech is fueled by Elemental Power, and attach it to the mine-carts in an effort to blast their way out of the mountain to confront the evil Skull Sorcerer!

added.title: Wasted True Potential
added.description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

added.title: Questing For Quests
added.description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

added.title: A Rocky Start
added.description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: The Belly of the Beast
added.description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
added.description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 3
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 4
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: Mumm-Ra of Plun-Darr Part 1
added.description: The Thundercats' worst nightmare comes true when their worst enemies, Mumm-Ra and The Mutants, team up after Mumm-Ra acquires The Sword of Plun-Darr!

added.title: Mumm-Ra of Plun-Darr Part 2
added.description: Chaos reigns over Third Earth now that the Mutants and Mumm-Ra control the Cats' Lair! The Thundercats' only hope is to sneak back in and get a super secret weapon Panthro has hidden at the heart of the Lair.

added.title: Guardian of the Unikingdom
added.description: Hawkodile insists the Unikingdom is more dangerous than it looks and sets out to prove it by taking his friends on bodyguard patrol.

added.title: Cast Aside the Truth
added.description: Hawkodile breaks his arm in a careless spill and lies to his friends about the accident to keep from looking bad.

added.title: Unikitty and the Ice Pop Factory
added.description: An eccentric figure announces a contest to tour her marvelous ice pop factory, sending the gang on a frantic quest to find the winning popsicle stick.

added.title: Halloween vs. Navidad
added.description: Cuando Santa Claus intenta apoderarse de Halloween, los Titanes necesitan a un par de espíritus para detenerlo.

added.title: Los Jovenes Titanes Salvan la Navidad
added.description: Santa renuncia a la Navidad, y los Titanes deben intervenir para salvar la festividad.

added.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
added.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

added.title: Buscando Misiones
added.description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

added.title: Un Comienzo Dificil
added.description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: El Vientre del Monstruo
added.description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
added.description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

added.title: Unboxing Part 1
added.description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

added.title: Unboxing Part 2
added.description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

added.title: Magnus P.I.
added.description: There's a been a string of thefts and each one has involved a Bakugan. The AAAnimus security force have decided the only brawler who could be responsible is: Magnus. The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

added.title: Awesome Brawlers Training  Camp
added.description: The Awesome Brawlers head to a training facility owned by Kasami International to prepare for the Bakugan Battle League - Los Volmos. But once the gang figures out they will all be competing against each other for the same title, the "team building" retreat doesn't quite go as planned./Agit turns up at the Kasami training facility and fits right in with the Awesome brawlers. This is a lifestyle that he can get used to, but it becomes apparent Agit is torn between a life as a phantom thief and life as a brawler.

added.title: The Bakugan Battle League Begins/Riot vs. Ajit
added.description: The Bakugan Battle League Begins: The qualifying rounds for the Bakugan Battle league are taking place all around Los Volmos. The Awesome Brawlers all make it through into the tournament without a hitch, that is all but Dan. Dan faces an old rival in Trey, who's back with a few tricks up his sleeve./Riot vs. Ajit: The Bakugan battle league is finally here and 16 brawlers have qualified to enter including all the Awesome Brawlers. The first round will feature a brawl between China Riot and the golden Bakugan brawler, Agit!

added.title: Kung Fu Master/A Battle of Popularity
added.description: Kung Fu Master: Dan's first match-up of the Bakugan battle league is the Chinese Champion Brawler: Zhao. His opponent is a deeply focused, and serious brawler, who uses Kung Fu techniques in battle. It's going to take all Dan and Drago's focus and strength to get through this opponent!/A Battle of Popularity: Shun and Wynton's first match-ups in the Bakugan battle league take place at the same time. Even though they're not battling each other, Wynton can't help getting a little competitive with Shun, bragging that he can get the crowd cheering louder than Shun. The brawls quickly turn into a popularity contest, instead of a Bakugan battle!

added.title: The Mysterious Revenger/Wynton vs. Lia
added.description: The Mysterious Revenger: It's the quarter finals of the Bakugan Battle League, the top eight brawlers are set to face off! In this round, Dan will face off against the Bakugan rocker - Revenger! These two brawlers give it their all in this icy cold clash!/Wynton Vs. Lia: The quarter finals continue, and it's the first Awesome Brawler vs. Awesome Brawler matches of the Bakugan Battle League tournament. In this round, it's Wynton vs. Lia and Shun vs. Lightning.

added.title: I.C.E. (In Case of Emergency)
added.description: When Ice Man decides to be a hero, Mega Man, influenced by Ice Man's literalness, steps down from the hero biz until a true crisis snaps him out of it.

added.title: Trust Your Guts, Man!
added.description: Guts Man tries to undo Dr. Light's eco-friendly disposal of trash in Silicon City by infiltrating the family and destroying the Lighthouse so he can eat it!

added.title: Drill of the Hunt
added.description: Mega Man tries a quick fix using Hypno Woman's powers to rehabilitate Drill Man, to disastrous results!

added.title: Power Cycle
added.description: After replicating Elec Man's powers, an underslept/overcharged Mega Man goes on a 24/7 hero spree that ends up turning him into his own worst enemy.

added.title: Bored to Be Wild
added.description: Mega Man teams up with his crush, Ashley Adderley, to solve a series of science riddles left by Chemical Man, who's plotting to turn all the city's metal into rubber.

added.title: The Quiet One
added.description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

added.title: Game of Masks
added.description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

added.title: Dread on Arrival
added.description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

added.title: True Potential
added.description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

added.title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
added.description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

added.title: The End of the Universe III Part 1
added.description: Windblade wakes the War Titan Iaconus, only to discover the Quintessons have a Titan of their own!

added.title: The End of the Universe III Part 2
added.description: Iaconus and Croaton do battle as Optimus, Bumblebee and Wheeljack contend with the Scientist.

added.title: The End of the Universe IV Part 1
added.description: With Iaconus down, the Cybertronians make a desperate last stand against Judge Starscream.

added.title: The End of the Universe IV Part 2
added.description: Megatron returns from the Multiverse with enough new found powers to contest Judge Starscream, Windblade uses all her power attempting to free Croaton from Quintesson control.

added.title: Enemy Line Part 1
added.description: While Optimus struggles to be a leader in peace-time, Bumblebee undertakes a daring mission into Decepticon territory.

added.title: Enemy Line Part 2
added.description: Bee recovers a comatose Windblade from Shadowstriker and must shepherd her safely from Decepticon territory.

added.title: El silencioso
added.description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Juego de mascaras
added.description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Terror llegando
added.description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: El verdadero potencial
added.description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
added.description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Molestando a los Bichos
added.description: El equipo de Tennyson viaja al Instituto Crisalín en busca de yoga a altas temperaturas y buenas vibraciones, solo para descubrir que los hermanos Bicho también están de vacaciones. Pero ¿los astutos insectoides están realmente de vacaciones, o están tramando otro de sus tontos planes?

added.title: Franken Pelea
added.description: Ben se sube al Rustbuggy para recibir una lección de conducción a lo largo de las dunas de Cabo Cod. Pero el plan da un extraño giro cuando el Rustbuggy se transforma en un monstruo motorizado por Bootleg, otra transformación alienígena de Kevin 11.

added.title: Cual Reloj?
added.description: Cuando una batalla con Kevin queda interrumpida, Ben se concentra en ser mejor que Gwen en el Campamento Espacial. Pero cuando Kevin regresa con la mirada extrañamente puesta en su prima, nuestro héroe debe descubrir quién está realmente detrás de todo esto: iCharmcaster!

added.title: Maiz Peleas
added.description: El equipo Tennyson descubre una reconstrucción del conflicto familiar Hartfield-McJoy en el maizal de al lado, pero cuando Hex resucita a los fantasmas de las verdaderas familias enemistadas, Ben debe encontrar la manera de reunirlos si quiere salvar a todos.

added.title: Bebe Baktu
added.description: Cuando es atacado en la jungla, el equipo Tennyson es salvado por un niño que se parece inquietantemente a Tim Buktu, pero cuando descubren que realmente es una versión en miniatura del infame trotamundos, Ben sabe que se avecina otra amenaza, Nanny Nightmare!

added.title: #LaDulceJusticia - Tercera parte
added.description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #La dulce justicia - Cuarta parte
added.description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 4 del episodio estreno.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Show de momias
added.description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

added.title: Unboxing Parte 1
added.description: Axel se aventura en el laboratorio de sótano estrictamente prohibido de su tío con la esperanza de arreglar un juguete roto y termina desatando a los vivos: iel renegado Madcap y todo un equipo de juguetes superpoderosos dedicados a detenerlo!

added.title: Unboxing Parte 2
added.description: Axel descubre que puede transformarse en un juguete y se une a su nuevo equipo de juguetes para evitar que Madcap robe una batería de Minergy.
